This paper discusses efficient training for neural network quantization, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also analyzes the gradient propagation process of neural networks, which is a topic related to neural networks (cs.NE) and robotics (cs.AR). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.AI, followed by cs.NE and cs.AR.
